title: Urban Coworking Airport
description: The first coworking lounge in South America, Urban Coworking Airport, is located within Guarulhos International Airport and has been structured to cater to tourists and executives passing through the area, where 40 million passengers from around the world circulate annually. Installed in the pre-boarding area of Terminal 2, its distinctive features include printing services, concierge, catering, showers, corporate training, a decompression area, and space for events.
